I should do a sweep.

355
00:25:35,213 --> 00:25:36,851
Yeah.

356
00:25:57,053 --> 00:25:59,123
Come on! I bruise easy.

357
00:25:59,293 --> 00:26:01,966
Gee, I wonder what color
you'll be when I'm done.

358
00:26:02,133 --> 00:26:03,361
Ow!

359
00:26:03,573 --> 00:26:05,609
Let's not, shall we?

360
00:26:05,773 --> 00:26:08,162
It's cool, dude. No worries.

361
00:26:08,333 --> 00:26:11,405
I don't remember anything.
I was drunk. I thought she was 18.

362
00:26:11,573 --> 00:26:14,610
Gonna work real hard on the
not-understanding-that, Lumpy.

363
00:26:14,773 --> 00:26:16,525
Francis!

364
00:26:16,733 --> 00:26:17,927
Ow!

365
00:26:18,413 --> 00:26:21,371
Break his head open.
See if there's any candy.

366
00:26:21,533 --> 00:26:24,650
- Hey, what do I look like, a pinata?
- Let's find out.

367
00:26:24,813 --> 00:26:27,930
Whoa, whoa! Ease off the contusion.
What do you want to know?

368
00:26:28,093 --> 00:26:31,165
- Where's Angelus?
- Who? Ow!

369
00:26:31,333 --> 00:26:35,167
We've been breathing stale beer and
blood half the night in pissholes like this.

370
00:26:35,333 --> 00:26:38,325
- Guess where it led us.
- I'm telling you, I don't know nothing.

371
00:26:38,493 --> 00:26:40,404
On my mother's tumor.

372
00:26:40,573 --> 00:26:44,122
And even if I did, I'd never yak
to a couple of fleshbags...

373
00:26:44,293 --> 00:26:47,524
...that are about to get their internal
organs sucked out of their...

374
00:26:50,093 --> 00:26:52,527
Strom demon.
Face should grow back.

375
00:26:54,253 --> 00:26:56,687
- Eventually.
- Think yours will?

376
00:26:57,173 --> 00:26:59,812
Oh, that Angelus. In here
all the time, running his mouth.

377
00:26:59,973 --> 00:27:03,329
"Look at me, I'm so evil." Jackass.
Never liked him. I'm on your side.

378
00:27:03,493 --> 00:27:05,643
Ow! Oh!

379
00:27:05,853 --> 00:27:08,890
- Where is he?
- I don't know, I swear.

380
00:27:09,053 --> 00:27:10,805
He was in here earlier...

381
00:27:10,973 --> 00:27:14,852
...and then he started mumbling
to himself like a big, pretty freak.

382
00:27:15,013 --> 00:27:17,925
