385
00:28:05,453 --> 00:28:08,013
- You okay?
- Dandy.

386
00:28:10,293 --> 00:28:12,284
[GROWLING]

387
00:28:18,613 --> 00:28:22,765
You know, most teenagers
check for pimples.

388
00:28:22,933 --> 00:28:24,412
I'm not...

389
00:28:24,893 --> 00:28:25,882
I wasn't...

390
00:28:26,293 --> 00:28:28,409
You tried to take him, didn't you?

391
00:28:28,573 --> 00:28:31,326
You attacked Angelus
inside the hotel...

392
00:28:31,493 --> 00:28:34,724
...and got spanked
by the anti-demon spell?

393
00:28:35,053 --> 00:28:36,725
