394
00:28:36,893 --> 00:28:38,645
I am.

395
00:28:38,933 --> 00:28:43,449
At least partly.
Kind of a pre-req for the visions gig.

396
00:28:43,613 --> 00:28:46,047
You chose that. It's not the same.

397
00:28:46,213 --> 00:28:47,805
Why not?

398
00:28:47,973 --> 00:28:50,567
I mean, why do l...?

399
00:28:51,533 --> 00:28:55,242
- Cordy, I don't even know what I am.
- I do.

400
00:28:55,933 --> 00:28:57,685
You're a daddy.

401
00:28:58,893 --> 00:29:02,124
And daddies need to take
responsibility, Connor.

402
00:29:03,013 --> 00:29:07,564
You need to face the fact
that we're special.

403
00:29:09,493 --> 00:29:12,053
Just like our baby's going to be.

404
00:29:17,493 --> 00:29:19,449
I'm really going to be a father.

405
00:29:20,373 --> 00:29:22,170
The best.

406
00:29:22,733 --> 00:29:26,851
And the only thing you ever
have to worry about...

407
00:29:27,693 --> 00:29:30,048
...is keeping us safe.

408
00:29:36,573 --> 00:29:40,248
So why don't you go back downstairs
and see what's going on?

409
00:29:40,413 --> 00:29:44,247
I'd feel a lot better if I knew
everything that was happening.

410
00:29:48,653 --> 00:29:50,325
FAITH: We're gonna get you
out of here.

411
00:29:50,493 --> 00:29:52,006
Faith.

412
00:29:52,173 --> 00:29:56,166
FAITH: Can you walk?
- No, but I can fly.

413
00:29:56,413 --> 00:29:58,881
- What did they do to her?
WESLEY: She did it to herself.

414
00:29:59,053 --> 00:30:02,966
They shoot up, the vampires feed.
Use them like a filter.

415
00:30:03,133 --> 00:30:06,284
I've read the effects can be quite
